lead_paragraph: Even before the Chicago Cubs got to celebrate their drought-ending World Series title with a parade, baseball's business season began Thursday when more than 100 players became free agents and teams started making decisions on 2017 options.

headline.print_headline: More Than 100 Become Free Agents as Business Season Starts
